              <h3>Share Your Thoughts</h3>
              <p>Create posts, share updates, and express yourself with our
                easy-to-use posting tools.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='feature-item'>
            <div class='feature-icon'>üë•</div>
            <div class='feature-content'>
              <h3>Connect with Others</h3>
              <p>Follow interesting people, build your network, and engage with
                content that matters to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='feature-item'>
            <div class='feature-icon'>üí¨</div>
            <div class='feature-content'>
              <h3>Engage & Interact</h3>
              <p>Like, comment, and bookmark posts. Join conversations and be
                part of the community.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='feature-item'>
            <div class='feature-icon'>üîî</div>
            <div class='feature-content'>
              <h3>Stay Updated</h3>
              <p>Get notifications about interactions, mentions, and activities
                from your network.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <div class='cta-container'>
          <a href='https://echo.app' class='cta-button'>Start Exploring Echo</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Tips Box -->
        <div class='tips-box'>
          <h3>üí° Quick Tips to Get Started</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Complete your profile to help others discover you</li>
            <li>Follow topics and people you're interested in</li>
            <li>Share your first post and introduce yourself</li>
            <li>Explore trending content and join conversations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class='divider'></div>

        <div class='message'>
          <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is
            here to help. Don't hesitate to reach out!</p>
          <p style='margin-top: 20px;'><strong>Happy exploring!</strong></p>
          <p>The Echo Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='footer-logo'>Echo</div>

        <div class='social-links'>
          <a href='https://twitter.com/echo'>Twitter</a>
          |
          <a href='https://facebook.com/echo'>Facebook</a>
          |
          <a href='https://instagram.com/echo'>Instagram</a>
        </div>

        <p><strong>&copy; {{year}} Echo.</strong> All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style='margin-top: 15px;'>This is an automated message. Please do not
          reply to this email.</p>
        <p>Need assistance?
          <a href='mailto:support@echo.app'>Contact Support</a></p>
        <p style='margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;'>
          <a href='https://echo.app/unsubscribe'>Unsubscribe</a>
          |
          <a href='https://echo.app/privacy'>Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href='https://echo.app/terms'>Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>